{"tid":2366404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國首相莊漢生：對中國保持警惕　但不要盲目反中","createTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T00:18:13.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0e794a4f95b69ccb7073e0e06f3dcd42a68c4bc7","tid":2366404,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"英國首相強生（Boris Johnson）周三（1/13）表示，英國應對中國參與其重要基礎設施保持警惕，但不該因此無腦反中。<br />\n<br />\n強生對國會專責委員會說，「我想強調，當我談到中國帶來的挑戰時，重要的是我們&hellip;應該保持警惕&hellip;我忍為我們必須對我們的重要國家基礎設施、保護我們的數據及網路空間保持十分警惕，而我們也非常警惕。」<br />\n<br />\n強生續指，「但我不想要這個國家或這個政府陷入一種無腦的反中立場。」，他補充，「必須保持平衡。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，強生表示，「我希望我們有個能與中國保持良好關係的世界，在那個世界，我們能夠與中國自由互動並坦承地與中國對話。說實話及譴責侵犯人權行為，不應阻礙我們在有可能的情況下，建立具成效的關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210114/XOKLINFQTZHN7NG4P26DZVASV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210114%2FXOKLINFQTZHN7NG4P26DZVASV4%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=f41fe1a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210114%2FXOKLINFQTZHN7NG4P26DZVASV4%2F&h=36461467\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210114/XOKLINFQTZHN7NG4P26DZVASV4/</a>"},{"pid":"ba75d0d254674a623e6d56fb96480fba1b32e838","tid":2366404,"uid":288707,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"即係縮啦"},{"pid":"0fb1acb64a1875c6285539c9eaaa36522e9e09b0","tid":2366404,"uid":4243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"說實話及譴責侵犯人權行為，不應阻礙我們在有可能的情況下，建立具成效的關係。<br />\n<br />\nWOW"},{"pid":"5ce9b200bba17eb1ef644b0672bea80da5dc7337","tid":2366404,"uid":251732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"當然唔好反中啦 因為我哋要滅中呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=